room_title: Escape room "Happy Campers" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_address: 611 N. Wilcox Street, Castle Rock, CO 80104
room_description: Ahh, the great outdoors…fresh air, the sounds of nature and a bear? Your camping sanctuary is being invaded by a hungry grizzly. He is circling your campsite and slowly closing in. You have to get out of here however, there’s one major problem; you can’t find the keys to the RV. You must scour the campsite, find the keys and escape before you become minced meat.
